OL,3,CHow Trump's oil blockade is pushing
OL,4,CCuba to the brink
OL,6,FITV News reports from the streets of
OL,7,FHavana as Donald Trump's oil embargo
OL,8,Fpushes Cubans further and further into
OL,9,Fcrisis.
OL,11,FBy US Correspondent Dan Rivers, with
OL,12,Fadditional reporting by Washington
OL,13,FNews Editor Jonathan Wald
OL,15,FIn Cuba, power is everything.
OL,17,FNot just the influence the Communist
OL,18,Fgovernment wields over the people, but
OL,19,Falso the electricity, vital for so
OL,20,Fmuch of modern life.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
