OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1781104294
OL,3,CHow Trump's oil blockade is pushing
OL,4,CCuba to the brink
OL,6,FCubans' ability to watch TV, read, and
OL,7,Flive with dignity is being suffocated.
OL,9,FThis comes amid the United States
OL,10,FNavy's decision to stop all oil
OL,11,Fimports from Central and South America.
OL,13,FThe American oil embargo has left the
OL,14,FCaribbean island in crisis, forcing
OL,15,Fthe local officials to choose which
OL,16,Fneighbourhoods to cut off and which to
OL,17,Fleave connected.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
