OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1781104294
OL,3,CHow Trump's oil blockade is pushing
OL,4,CCuba to the brink
OL,6,FThe Trump administration wants to
OL,7,Fcoerce Cuba into accepting sweeping
OL,8,Freforms, making it more aligned with
OL,9,Fthe US and less aligned with countries
OL,10,Flike Russia.
OL,12,FLast month, John Ratcliffe, the head
OL,13,Fof the CIA, held a summit with senior
OL,14,FCuban officials, delivering a stark
OL,15,Fmessage: Allow real change or face
OL,16,Fmilitary intervention.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
