CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1781104294
OL,3,CHow Trump's oil blockade is pushing
OL,4,CCuba to the brink
OL,6,FDonald Trump said in March that he
OL,7,Fthinks he will have the "honour of
OL,8,Ftaking Cuba" and has repeated his
OL,9,Fthreats to topple the Communist
OL,10,Fgovernment with increasing regularity.
OL,12,FYet Cuba's president, Miguel Diaz-
OL,13,FCanel, remains intransigent - and
OL,14,Fordinary Cubans are paying the price.
OL,16,FPetrol is rationed to 20 litres a
OL,17,Fmonth per person, but on the black
OL,18,Fmarket, if they can find it, Cubans
OL,19,Fare paying more than #5 a litre for
OL,20,Fpetrol.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
