OL,3,CHow Trump's oil blockade is pushing
OL,4,CCuba to the brink
OL,6,FIn a country where the health service
OL,7,Fwas once the apple of its eye, the
OL,8,Fsystem is now creaking under the
OL,9,Fpressure of the American blockade.
OL,11,FThere is a flourishing black market in
OL,12,Fmedicines advertised brazenly online
OL,13,Fby medical workers selling what they
OL,14,Fcan steal from hospitals.
OL,16,FWith Cuba less capable of producing
OL,17,Fits own sustenance, shipments of food
OL,18,Fand relief supplies are a vital
OL,19,Flifeline.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
