OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1781104294
OL,3,CHow Trump's oil blockade is pushing
OL,4,CCuba to the brink
OL,6,FWe watched as a Panamanian-flagged
OL,7,Fvessel from Mexico arrived with 7,000
OL,8,Ftonnes of milk, beans and rice.
OL,10,FIt will help with the hardship, but
OL,11,Fnot with the power.
OL,13,FOne Russian oil tanker was permitted
OL,14,Fto dock, but its cargo wasn't nearly
OL,15,Fenough to make any meaningful
OL,16,Fdifference to the crisis.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
