OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1781104294
OL,3,CHow Trump's oil blockade is pushing
OL,4,CCuba to the brink
OL,6,FIt's still haunted by its failed
OL,7,Fmission at the Bay of Pigs in 1961
OL,8,Fwhen John F. Kennedy's attempt to
OL,9,Fdefeat Fidel Castro's men ended in
OL,10,Fhumiliation for the Americans.
OL,12,FCould the US, buoyed by its success in
OL,13,Fabducting Venezuelan President Nicolas
OL,14,FMaduro, attempt to snatch and put on
OL,15,Ftrial Castro's brother, 95-year-old
OL,16,FRaul, who was recently indicted by the
OL,17,FUS?
OL,19,FTrump may opt for a campaign of
OL,20,Fairstrikes to decapitate the regime,
OL,21,Fstarting with its current president.
OL,26,@uD@erpxD@Crz
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
