OL,3,CHow Trump's oil blockade is pushing
OL,4,CCuba to the brink
OL,6,FWhile he deliberates on what action to
OL,7,Ftake and when to take it, many Cubans
OL,8,Fare losing patience with their own
OL,9,Fgovernment and its inability to
OL,10,Festablish any kind of resilience.
